            "title": "港股午後跌幅擴大 暫跌263點或1.02% 科指挫2.05%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後繼續試底，截至下午約2時08分，恒生指數已跌263點或1.02%，報25662點；恒生科技指數跌幅更達2.05%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今日掛牌的曦智科技(01879)午後則更上層樓，暫報919點，較招股價183.2元高4.02倍；每手賬面暫賺1.1萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15932001-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%9a%ab%e8%b7%8c263%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%961-02-%e7%a7%91%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab2-05",
