            "title": "中滙集團半年倒退58.4% 不派中期息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中滙集團(00382)公布，截至今年2月底止半年公司擁有人應佔利潤為1.01億元(人民幣‧下同)，較去年同期的2.44億元倒退58.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內收入11.86億元，也較去年同期的11.47億元減少4.9%。董事會不擬派中期息。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15931389-%e4%b8%ad%e6%bb%99%e9%9b%86%e5%9c%98%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e5%80%92%e9%80%8058-4-%e4%b8%8d%e6%b4%be%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/00382-Web.jpg.webp",
