        {
            "title": "半日收市︱抽水顧慮 恒指跌173點報25752點 寧德時代藍籌包尾 藥明康德績後強勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">隨著多家公司爭相配股或換股債向市場「抽水」，港股今早借勢再回吐。寧德時代(03750)曾失守配股價，藥明康德(02359)績後則強勢畢現。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早全程報跌，甫開市已失守52天線(最新約為25888點)，於早段出現的半日高位25896點時仍跌28點，中段跌幅重新擴大至逾百點，半日低位25729點時跌196點，其後便於20天線(最新約為25752點)附近爭持。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250527_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250527_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250527_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指中午收報25752點，跌173點或0.67%。恒生科技指數跑輸大市，半日跌60點或1.23%，報4879點；國企指數也跌82點或0.94%，報8673點。主板半日成交1311.91億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">明天將是期指結算，即月期指今早跌150點，報25780點，高水27點。科指期貨跌55點，報4885點，高水6點。國指期貨跌80點，報8679點，高水5點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">傳聞多時的寧德時代50億美元配股，終於在昨天收市後開始，最終以配股範圍下限628.2元定價，較該股昨收市價折讓約7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">消息公布後，寧德時代今早一如意料裂口低開，以630元開市，跌6.74%，其後反覆整固，但半日高位631.5元時仍跌6.51%，於低位613.5元時更挫9.18%；中午收報629元，跌6.88%，險守配股價，但仍是表現最差藍籌，交投63.36億元，在主板股份成交額榜排第2位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他宣布集資的公司，今早股價亦跌多升少。中國宏橋(01378)則擬發102億元人民幣的1年期零息換股債，雖然換股價較該股昨天收市價有多達逾25%，該股今早依然受壓，半日跌3.54%，報33.8元，在藍籌中表現排在尾三。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於其他公布配股的公司中，以361度(01361)跌勢最明顯，中午收報5.57元，挫19.51%；達力普(01921)輕微高開後迅速倒跌，中午收報5.27元，亦挫12.17%。博泰車聯(02889)以折讓價10.19%配股予獨立第三方、由曹暉擁有的三鋒控股，該股今早表現反覆，中午收報145.1元，升2.54%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股同樣跌多升少，「ATMXJ」全線報跌，當中以小米(01810)較弱，雖然獲高盛及摩根士丹利相繼發報告唱好，小米的旗艦大模型MiMo-V2.5-Pro及全模態模型MiMo-V2.5又宣布正式全球開源，該公司又同步推出MiMo Orbit計劃，涵蓋百萬億Token創造者激勵計劃，小米今早股價仍跌2.44%，報30.34元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250527_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250527_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在「ATMXJ」餘下4位成員中，騰訊(00700)跌勢較輕微，中午收報476.4元，跌0.46%，以62.43億元交投成主板成交額最多股份；京東(09618)跌0.86%，報116元；美團(03690)跌1.22%，報80.85元。阿里巴巴(09988)擬分拆嘉興園區於深圳以基礎設施REIT方式上市，已獲港交所(00388)批准；阿里巴巴今早仍幾乎全程報跌，中午收報127.6元，跌2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地車股亦受壓，將於今日收市後派成績表的比亞迪(01211)，績前股價跌1.13%，報104.8元，同系比亞迪電子(00285)更挫2.82%，報26.9元。吉利汽車(00175)跌2.59%，報21.8元；理想汽車(02015)跌2.8%，報67.75元；蔚來(09866)跌1.06%，報49.62元；小鵬汽車(09868)跌1.32%，報63.35元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩大藍籌國際金融股則負責撐市，滙控(00005)微升0.07%，報140.3元；友邦(01299)高開後反覆偏好，中午收報83.65元，升0.54%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不少績優股亦未有被當前市場的「抽水潮」誤傷，藥明康德(02359)績後獲券商唱好，該股今早應聲彈升並創逾3年新高，中午收報144.8元，飆14.92%，穩坐藍籌升幅榜首；同系藥明生物(02269)也升2.4%，報34.08元，在藍籌升幅榜排第3名。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">海爾智家(06690)昨公布的首季業績雖然盈利倒退，但公司承諾未來分紅+回購及註銷策略，支撐該股今早低開後迅速轉升，最高曾見21.68元，漲3.93%；中午收報21.42元，升2.69%，成表現次佳藍籌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價持續高踞不下，中海油(00883)收市後派季績前股價造好，半日升1.41%，報28.84元。「三桶油」其餘兩股今早則偏軟，中國石油(00857)中午收報11.43元，跌0.26%；中國石化(00386)跌0.22%，報4.61元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，今日有兩隻新股掛牌，半日均高收。曦智科技(01879)中午收報842元，較招股價183.2元高3.6倍；邁威生物(02493)中午收報28元，較招股價27.64元高1.3%。</p>\n</div>",
