            "title": "A股偏軟  深股曾跌1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股窄幅偏軟，深股曾跌逾1%，兩市成交合計16615.49億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-17.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日收報4083點，跌2點或0.07%，今早以4076點開市，跌10點或0.25%，早段見4090點，升4點或0.09%，為半日高位，後段見4074點，跌12點或0.29%，為半日低位，半日成交7273.28億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日跌60點或0.41%，報14934點，今早開市報14925點，跌70點或0.47%，最低見14831，跌158點或1.05%，為半日低位，其後向上，跌幅收窄至54點或0.36%，報14941，半日成交9342.21億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日跌19點或0.54%，報3629點，今早開跌13點或0.29%，開報4757點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日跌19點或0.54%，報3629點，今早開市報3623點，跌25點或0.69%。</p>\n</div>",
